<div class="login-box" style="width: 75%;">
    <div class="login-logo">
        <b>Reset Password</b>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center">
        Enter your secret code here along with your new password.<br/>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-1">
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="box box-primary">
            <div class="box-header with-border">

            </div>
            <!-- /.box-header -->
            <!-- form start -->
            <form class="form-horizontal">
                <div class="box-body">
                    <div class="form-group required">
                        <label class="col-sm-4 control-label">Your New Password</label>

                        <div class="col-sm-8">
                            {{input type="password" class="form-control" value=model.password placeholder="Password"}}
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group required">
                        <label class="col-sm-4 control-label">Confirm Your Password</label>

                        <div class="col-sm-8">
                            {{input type="password" class="form-control" value=model.password_confirm placeholder="Password"}}
                        </div>
                    </div>


                    <div class="form-group required">
                        <label class="col-sm-4 control-label">Secret Code</label>

                        <div class="col-sm-8">


                            <div class="input-group">
                                {{input type="text" class="form-control" value=model.code placeholder="#####"}}

                                {{#input-tooltip content="Check your email for the secret code.  Don't forget to check your spam folder if it isn't in your inbox."}}
                                    {{fa-icon "info"}}
                                {{/input-tooltip}}
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- /.box-body -->

                <div class="box-footer clearfix">
                    {{#link-to 'auth.reminder' class="btn btn-primary"}}Resend Secret Code{{/link-to}}
                    <button class="btn btn-primary pull-right" {{action "reset" model}}>Reset My Password</button>
                </div>
                <!-- /.box-footer -->

            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-1">
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-3">

        <div class="callout callout-info">
            <h4>What makes for a good password?</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>More than 8 characters</li>
                <li>Made of upper and lower case letters, numbers and symbols</li>
                <li>Avoid using words in your password, it makes it easier to crack.</li>
            </ul>


            <h4>The most common <strong>weak</strong> passwords are:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>123456</li>
                <li>password</li>
                <li>12345</li>
                <li>12345678</li>
                <li>qwerty</li>
            </ul>
            (so don't use these!)
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="col-md-1">
    </div>

</div>